\title{
Using Dempster-Shafer Theory for the combination of evidence
}
\description{
An R package for the use of Dempster-Shafer Theory for combination of evidence.
}
\details{
\tabular{ll}{
Package: \tab dst\cr
Type: \tab Package\cr
Version: \tab 1.0.0\cr
