The following operations can be done:
\describe{
  \item{Basic chance assignment}{Statement of a chance
assignments over subsets of the frame of discernment.}
  \item{Dempster's rule}{Combination of two belief functions and normalization}
  \item{belief/plausibility calculations}{Calculation of the measures of belief and plausibility on a belief function}
  \item{Plausibility ratio}{Calculation of the plausibility transformation and the ratio of plausibility of all the elements of a belief function}
  \item{Measure of conflict}{Calculation of the measure of conflict on a serie of beliefs functions combined by Dempster's rule}
}
}
